    {
      "chinese": "曾經聽耆老說過，我們汶水泰雅族群來說，較少遷居現象。某一天，跟Baycu’爺爺聊天，聊從小時候到老、農耕、生活等等，無所不談。他說汶水族群原本安居於後龍，自外來的閩南人外來並搶佔我們原本生活的領域，且族人又沒有能力抵禦外侮，即便心有不甘，也只能節節敗退而移居深山。說著說著，憶起從前生活上的點點滴滴，老人家眼眶不禁泛淚。",
      "ab": "pinungan mu tikay ku nanabakis mha “ukas cuqaang a pinughian na asigi ita’ ka Matu’uwal”. riax ka qutux, musa’ ci maskakaru’ ki yutas Baycu’, aring cu hbu ruu’ cu nabakis, papinumuwa’, kinqiyanux... ukas a ini’ niyam paskakaruani, minbalballayq ti maqiyanux i Holung ka Matu’uwal mhama, muwah kumawp ku Kamciyulang lru ingacan cami niya’ cu qaqiynuxan, anauwi ga bali kiya a rngu’ niyam i cumru’ ru magagaang cami magiyay inuinu’ ga, papgiyayun cami kiya cku mini’iyani niyam qawnam, ruu’ asi cami lau langaag i ragraggiyax. sipanqaquu’ niya’ ku wawwaw ka inuwahan na Nanabakis ga, maimag makasiun ca rawweq niya’ ku booq na rawweq.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2023/03/10/61ad7bbcf7465df4bb1e5e73bd7073b9.wav",
